title: Someone Unexpected Wants To Set Bobby Up On A Date + Amy Lets Down A Listener That Was Counting On Her

description:
Bobby is finally going to let someone set him up on a date, and you’ll never guess who. Amy lets a listener down who was depending on her for an awesome prize. Also, Lunchbox guesses callers’ weights just by talking to them on the phone.
